Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.22,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,到京都了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:04.01,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这就是传说中让人往下跳的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:05.77,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,让谁跳下去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:06.97,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么 在下就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.48,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不要乱来…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:10.49,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这就是清水寺的本堂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:13.04,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,也就是俗称的「清水之舞台」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:18.49,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,本来是为供奉的观音菩萨像 表演能剧和舞蹈而建造
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:18.49,zhushi,,0,0,0,,(注：能剧为一种日本的传统戏剧)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:20.44,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,已经被列为国宝级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:24.16,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,有句名句叫「打算从清水之舞台跳下去」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:28.31,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,在江户时代就有234次跳下去的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:31.01,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,存活率居然意外的达到了85%之多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:32.79,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊…真是个奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:35.91,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,夕映可是神社 寺庙 佛像的发烧友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.42,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我们是在「修学旅行」 里面有个「学」字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:41.80,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,也就是说这也是教学的一环
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:45.46,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,各位同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:48.14,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,能够一起来 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:55.59,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 修学旅行真是太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:03:00.41,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 如果高畑老师也能一起来就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:01.68,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:04.05,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,他是一年级的班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.30,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:07.80,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,涅吉 一起去抽签吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:09.80,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊…啊…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:12.44,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:20.35,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真怀念呢 小刹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.05,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好久没回京都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:26.29,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,喏 和当初我们两个人一起玩时没怎么变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:31.44,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那个时候每天每天都玩得好高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:33.95,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那时我们还没有上学…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:35.88,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,先失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:41.15,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,小刹…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.50,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,现在那些家伙在清水寺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.36,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真是遗憾呢 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:52.28,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,您因为登校地狱的诅咒而不能去修学旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:54.71,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,喂 有什么可遗憾的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:56.91,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,倒是你自己去不好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:04:00.64,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不 我想要一直陪伴在主人身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:02.17,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:08.73,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 快看啊 是缘分占卜的神社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.72,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 快去快去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:14.71,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,30分钟后要回入口处集合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:17.69,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大哥大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:18.48,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.84,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这个交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:21.93,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:23.63,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,学院长爷爷拜托的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.67,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,遇到困难的时候可以靠这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.81,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这是…要送到关西咒术协会总部的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:32.32,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,还有介绍信…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:35.77,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,咦？关西咒术协会不是敌人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:39.86,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不是的 只是其中叫做封眼寺派的一部分人在惹事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:42.01,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,关西咒术协会本身…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:44.95,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,涅吉 快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:47.51,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,有恋爱占卜石哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:54.09,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,咦？只要闭上眼睛 从这块石头走到那块石头的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:55.78,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,恋爱就会顺利是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:56.49,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好远
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:59.15,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,差不多有20米远吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:02.45,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么就由身为班长的我开始吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:05.05,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 好狡猾哦 我也要走过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:06.62,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:07.82,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:09.60,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.04,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,书店 不是那边啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:17.43,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,虽然对不起大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:18.82,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但这种程度的试练
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:22.14,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,对精通各种武艺 并取得了各种段位证明的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:23.50,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,根本就不算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.83,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,雪广绫香流·恋爱心眼术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:34.75,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:36.14,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,等等 班长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:37.78,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,班长耍赖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:38.71,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:42.30,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这样涅吉老师和我的将来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.23,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,就能够确定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:45.41,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:47.84,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这…这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.77,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好像踩到了软软的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:53.18,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:58.17,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊！青青青…青蛙！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:04.43,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,青蛙？怎么这么多…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.27,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大哥 不要放松	警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:08.47,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这可能只是在分散我们的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:09.69,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,咦？那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.59,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 太好了 信还在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:15.51,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:16.60,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不好了 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:17.57,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.80,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大哥 那是「式神」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:20.80,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,「式神」？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:23.44,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是啊 日本的一种召唤魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:25.30,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不 应该说是纸制的魔偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:38.07,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.36,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊？樱咲同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:41.70,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这是我拣到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.63,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 那是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:46.26,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的好意…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.29,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,小心一些会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:53.16,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这里是京都 可不是麻帆良学院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:56.62,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,喂喂 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:58.60,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你为什么要感谢她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.36,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.25,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.12,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,刚才那只鸟的纸型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:05.43,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,也就是说她是施术者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:07.70,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,怎么会…樱咲同学她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:12.40,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,她很可能是我们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.28,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,夕映 要出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:34.73,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.03,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我们来玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:43.14,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,和香 明天的自由时间你要干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:44.50,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:46.24,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,和涅吉老师一起逛京都吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:50.96,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,枕头大战是一定要玩的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.17,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,一定要玩一定要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:02.74,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,咦？樱咲同学是敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.84,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不 只是怀疑而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:08.48,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不会错的 她就是封眼寺派的手下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:10.05,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:15.35,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是 听说樱咲同学和木乃香是青梅竹马啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:17.15,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,咦？是那样的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:20.71,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是 没见过那两个人彼此说过话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:23.28,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,木乃香的确这样说过的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.51,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,总之 危机就近在眼前了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:30.19,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,所以想请大姐来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:31.21,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.40,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大姐 这个还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:36.90,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 是我和明日菜同学定下暂订契约的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:40.53,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊…不要让我回想起那种害羞的事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:41.35,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:44.08,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这可不是普通的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:47.57,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大姐只要念「阿德阿特」 就可以变出武器！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:47.57,yingwen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(272,410)}Adeat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.17,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:52.18,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你想让我参加战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.79,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不行 不行啦 对手可是会用魔法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.73,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我只是普通的女中学生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:01.54,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不是不是 最近的女中学生不容小看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:03.02,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,特别是在这2-A里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:05.84,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,确实 依文洁琳同学和枫同学都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:07.09,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,…啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.34,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:17.11,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,对不起 不知道为什么没有反应…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:20.85,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,唔 真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:25.44,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这种时候 直接用手就可以了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:28.28,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真不愧是大姐 完全是蛮力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:29.19,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:32.42,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真是不好意思 太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.77,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不用 是不是出故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:38.88,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真伤脑筋呢 我会和旅馆的人说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.50,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真是谢谢你放我进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:50.98,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,可爱的西洋魔法使先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:59.07,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,喔喔 这个就梦幻商品抹茶可乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:02.34,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,夕映还是这么喜欢奇怪的饮料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:03.02,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:05.87,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这是小刹喜欢的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:07.94,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,去哪里啊 木乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.94,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我去告诉小刹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:11.88,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,小刹？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:13.77,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:19.85,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好厉害 这就是露天浴场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:22.61,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,被风吹着真舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:26.67,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没错 要是没有关于樱咲刹那的烦心事就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.48,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:33.22,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是哪位老师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:38.74,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,樱…樱咲同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:40.73,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这里不是男浴场么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:42.87,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这里是混浴啊 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:47.55,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好的 这样结界就布置完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:49.63,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,在干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.36,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,快逃吧 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.78,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,她可是剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:56.10,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没有伙伴的近身战对大哥十分不利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:57.28,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:59.44,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但话说回来还是不好办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:03.99,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,本来还指望作为魔法使的老师 能够做点什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:05.61,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:07.70,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,为什么知道我是魔法使的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.57,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,刹那那家伙 果然是敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:15.73,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.03,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,糟了 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:18.58,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,想逃走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:21.76,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,神鸣流奥义·斩岩剑！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:28.17,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大哥 救命！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:29.14,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,卡莫！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:33.05,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,拉斯泰尔·马斯吉尔·马吉斯泰尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:33.05,yingwen,,0,0,0,,ras tel ma scir magister
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:35.67,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,风花·武装解除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:35.67,yingwen,,0,0,0,,FLANS  EXARMATIO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.65,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,厉害 大哥把那家伙的武器击落了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:43.65,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你是什么人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.58,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不回答的话就捏烂掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:56.92,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你是什么人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:59.03,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不回答的话就捏烂掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:03.22,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 涅吉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:06.28,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,对…对不起 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:11.57,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不…这只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.73,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我工作中理论上是一定要攻击要害的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:19.17,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,樱咲刹那！你这家伙果然是封眼寺派的手下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.69,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,什么…不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:24.64,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,现在证据确凿了 你给我准备好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:26.01,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我不是敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:28.01,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我和老师同一阵线的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:36.60,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,小刹如果看到那个点心的话一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.07,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,欢迎到来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:51.45,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,刚才的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:52.61,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大小姐的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.61,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,咦 猴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:58.70,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,明日菜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:00.14,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,木乃香大小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:07.92,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,只要把木乃香大小姐夺到手 我们就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.19,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.48,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,太过纠缠的话会被讨厌的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.79,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,坏了 要逃进车站了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:20.59,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.59,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,虽然是停运时间 但怎么连一个站务人员都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:25.76,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,她张贴了不让人靠近的符咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:28.56,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,敌人的目标是木乃香大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.67,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是一开始就计划好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.40,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,为什么要针对木乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:34.91,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,木乃香大小姐她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.39,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,潜藏有极东地区最强的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:39.64,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:42.40,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,甚至能与Thousand master相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:43.65,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.78,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,魔力的话…那就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.87,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,木乃香大小姐是魔法使吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.26,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大小姐自己并没意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:53.29,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是 敌人看来已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:58.95,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,涅吉老师 把她逼到前面的车厢去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:09.40,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,符咒啊符咒 帮助我摆脱对方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.19,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这些水是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:27.41,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊哈哈…可别淹死在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:32.14,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不妙 居然被敌人这样轻易的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.31,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我的技术…果然还不够成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.65,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,木乃香大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:42.94,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,小刹 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:47.45,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,斩空闪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.70,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,还很不错的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.57,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不过 我可不会把大小姐还给你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.04,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,木乃香大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:02.99,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.95,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,把木乃香大小姐还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.90,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,哟 居然能追到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.80,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不过 也只能到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:28.56,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,封眼寺派的么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:34.67,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,符咒啊符咒 帮助我摆脱对方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:36.01,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.12,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:40.20,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,三枚符咒术·京都大文字烧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:46.16,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:49.31,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,能力普通的施术者 是没办法穿过这些火焰的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.84,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,拉斯泰尔·马斯吉尔·马吉斯泰尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.84,yingwen,,0,0,0,,ras tel ma scir magister
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.78,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,风花·风尘乱舞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.78,yingwen,,0,0,0,,FLANS  SALTATIO  PULVEREA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:02.80,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我的火焰居然被吹灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.61,0:16:06.14,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这就是西洋魔法使的力量吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.17,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,把大小姐还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:20.23,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这种招式…神鸣流？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:23.07,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真对不起 我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:29.86,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你好 我是神鸣流的 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.85,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你也是…神鸣流剑士？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.92,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是的 我叫月咏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:40.45,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,看上去您也是神鸣流的前辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:42.64,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不过既然我被雇来做护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.82,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,还是要全力以赴的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:49.60,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这种事情神鸣流也做…时代也变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:50.61,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.23,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,太小看她的话可使会受伤的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:53.78,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,月咏小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:57.75,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是的 那么我就上了 请手下留情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:07.61,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,出乎意外的强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:09.40,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,刹那同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:12.51,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,喂 你们的对手在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:16.52,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,小熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:18.53,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:19.84,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,布偶自己在动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:22.84,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,请小心一点 从外表上是看不出它们很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.42,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,拉斯泰尔·马斯吉尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.42,yingwen,,0,0,0,,ras tel ma scir…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:25.84,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,拉斯泰尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:25.84,yingwen,,0,0,0,,ras tel…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:27.34,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,拉斯泰尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:27.34,yingwen,,0,0,0,,ras tel…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:33.74,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈 我的猿鬼和熊鬼可是很强的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:37.01,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,坏了 即使是大哥以一敌二的话也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.19,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好色雪貂 那咒文是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.02,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:42.43,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,喂 能变出武器的那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:44.63,yingwen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(307,410)}Adeat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:44.63,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 是「阿德阿特」啊 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.30,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:48.06,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,阿德阿特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:48.06,yingwen,,0,0,0,,Adeat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:55.15,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:56.91,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:58.82,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,只不过是把折扇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:00.23,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,咦 哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:03.65,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大姐的卡片上的确写的是「破魔之剑」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:04.95,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:08.50,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没办法了 上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:16.51,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:20.88,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那是什么 我的猿鬼居然被送回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:21.83,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:23.11,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.33,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但这只熊就交给我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:25.47,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你去救木乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:26.35,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:27.32,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.39,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,拉斯泰尔·马斯吉尔·马吉斯泰尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.39,yingwen,,0,0,0,,ras tel ma scir magister
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:32.73,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,魔法之射手·警戒之风矢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:32.73,yingwen,,0,0,0,,SAGITTA  MAGICA,AER  CAPTURAE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:37.04,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:38.18,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:42.34,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:46.32,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,快放开木乃香同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:47.52,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:50.20,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,呵呵 你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:52.51,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,竟然因为顾及人质而不攻击我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:57.69,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊哈哈…这个女孩还真有用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.97,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,既可以作人质
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:02.49,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,还可以作「发电机」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:03.96,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你说「发电机」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:07.44,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是啊 只要用咒术和符咒让她听话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:10.27,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,按我们的意愿释放魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:13.02,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,就可以成为我们的魔力发电机了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:15.03,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.93,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我赢定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:22.15,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,还有 不听话的小鬼可要打屁股哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:27.87,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,居然对木乃香大小姐…做这种事！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:29.84,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:32.65,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,秘剑·百花撩乱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:42.54,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:45.16,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.29,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,小刹？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:01.50,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:04.01,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 小刹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:06.62,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,虽然不清楚出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:07.96,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是你救了我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:12.10,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我…我失礼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:13.00,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:16.00,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:17.89,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:19.06,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,小刹？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:20.80,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,刹那同学 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:41.42,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,被你救了呢 新人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.90,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,眼镜眼镜 我的眼镜…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:42.62,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,有一手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:50.84,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,Thousand master的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:53.35,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,只有那种程度而已吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:10.17,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊 喂喂 我是近右卫门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.88,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,哦 是刹那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:17.90,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,什么？封眼寺派的咒术使？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:23.12,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不…只是现在要立刻派增援过去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:24.36,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:23:00.56,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,喂 班长会合气道对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.68,0:23:04.31,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,嗯 不过仅仅达到了「免许皆传」的程度而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.68,0:23:04.31,zhushi,,0,0,0,,(免许皆传：级别的一种，强于「上级」)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:06.73,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,能不能教给我一些简单的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.83,0:23:08.84,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么先教一些小技巧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:11.10,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,就是扳住腰和腿再投掷出去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:13.82,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,扳住吗…我知道了 做做试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.63,0:23:15.73,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,搞什么搞！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.82,0:23:19.80,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,想让我把手从你嘴里伸进去捏碎你的喉*吗 笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.84,0:23:22.92,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,莳绘同学 这可就不是「扳住」而是「切断」了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.07,0:23:24.15,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你说什么？！

